quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  33,60,"Ne Abeshikhabili nende balia bali nende obulwale mumioyo chiabu nende balia abasalasinjia obubii mulukongo, nibalalekha tawe, toto khwitsa okhubasasiakhwo ewe, ne shibetsa okhwikhala omo ahambi ninawe halali khubise bititi butswa"
  33,61,"Batsubwa, wosiwosi abalolekhana batilwe mana berwe okhwirwa"
  33,62,"Liba lia Nyasaye alialiwo khubalia babura, ne sholinyoola muliba lia Nyasaye obukalukhani tawe"
  33,63,"Abandu bakhurebanga okhulondokhana nende indukho, boola mbu: “ obumanyi bwayo bulikhu Nyasaye butswa, ne nishina shitsa okhumanyisia mbu indukho ili ahambi.”"
  33,64,Toto Nyasaye yatsuba Abakhayi ne nabarecheshela omulilo
  33,65,"Balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsiosi, neshibalinyoolamwo Omuhelwa nohomba omukhonyi tawe"
  33,66,"Inyanga yobweni bwabu bulikalukhanibwa mumulilo baliboola mbu: “Abaane manyanga khuwulila Nyasaye, mana khuwulila Omurumwa.”"
  33,67,"Ne baliboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu toto efwe khwaulila Abaami befu, nende Abakhongo befu, mana abo nibakhukosia injila.”"
  33,68,"Nyasaye wefu bahelesie bano eshinyasio shimetekhe, ne obatsube eshitsubo eshikhongo"
  33,69,"Enywe Abasuubila mulaba shinga balia abasinyisia Musa, mana Nyasaye namutswenula khukababoola, naye yali weshiribwa imbeli wa Nyasaye"
  33,70,Enywe balia basuubila murie Nyasaye ne muboole amakhuwa katoto
  33,71,"Alabakasilia obulayi ebikhole bienyu ne alabaleshela ebionoono bienyu, ne ulia uwulila Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, toto alaba naburire okhubura okhukhonga"
  33,72,"Toto efwe khwalolesia omalako kefu likulu nende eshialo nende tsingulu, mana nibikhaya okhukachinga nibiria, ne nikhubilolela tsimbabaasi mana Omundu nachinga. Toto ye ni omwonooni omukhongo omusilu muno"
  33,73,"Kho Nyasaye anyoole okhuhelesia eshinyasio abeshikhabili, Abasatsa nende abeshikhabili Abakhasi, Nende abatsokaasi beshisatsa nende Abatsokaasi beshikhasi, Ne aleshele abasubili abasatsa nende abasubili abakhasi, ne toto Nyasaye ni omulesheli muno owetsimbabaasi po"
  34,1,"Oluyali lwosi ni lwa Nyasaye, ulia owebili mwikulu nende mushialo nebibie, ne mwikulu oluyali nolulwe, naye ni Owamachesi Omumanyi muno"
  34,2,"Amanyile kenjilanga mwiloba nende karulangamwo, nende kekhanga mwikulu nende kaninagamwo, naye ni Omulesheli muno, Owetsimbabaasi po"
  34,3,"Ne abakhayi baboola mbu: “indukho eyo shilikhwitsila tawe,” Boola mbu: “khushina? Nditsuba khu Nyasaye wanje, toto ilibetsela, Omumanyi wakefisile, sishifisanga khuye tawe kata eshili nende obusiru shinga bweyindukusi, mwikulu nohomba khushialo, nohomba eshititi okhushila esho, nohomba eshikhongo muno, halali biosi ebo bili mushitabu shinoosinjia.”"
  34,4,"Abarunje balia abasuubila mana nibakhola ebikhole ebilayi, abo balinyoola obulesheli nende omukabo kwoluyali"
  34,5,"Ne balia bakhalabana okhuyingasia ebimanyisio biefu, nibalola mbu besta okhukhushila, abo balinyoola eshinyasio eshibii shiobululu"
  34,6,"Ne balia bahebwa obumanyi, bamanya mbu kalia keshibwa khwiwe okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo nikatoto, nako kalunjisinjia khunjila ya Owamaani witsomibungwa muno"
  34,7,"Ne balia abakhaya baboola mbu: “ koo khubechesiekhwo Omusatsa ubaboolelanga mbu olwamuliba nimurandulwe (nimubolele) ebitonye ebitonye mbu mulikalusibwa mwaba ebiloonje obiyiakha?”"
  34,8,“Koo yakhaba nachiishile Nyasaye obubeyi nohomba ali nende lilalu?” Halali balia abalasubila mwikulu tawe bali mushinyasio nende obukori bwa ehale muno
  34,9,"Koo, shibalolangakhwo akali imbeli wabu nende akali inyuma wabu akelikulu nende eshialo? Khwenyanga khwakhalomesiye liloba liabamila, nohomba khwakhabakwisiyiekhwo ebitonye bielikulu, toto mu ako khulimwo nende abimanyisio khubuli Omusumba, Owekanila. (yasaba eshileshelo)"